---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="About CFCON â€” Atlassian Consulting and Marketplace App development.">
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About CFCON</h1>

      <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <div class="space-y-6 text-text-light leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-lg">
            CFCON is an Atlassian-focused consulting firm and software vendor. We combine hands-on Atlassian expertise with purpose-built apps to help organizations work more effectively.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl p-8 my-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-6">What drives us</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Practitioner mindset</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">We build tools we use ourselves. Every app comes from real pain points we've encountered in production Atlassian environments.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Security first</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">All our apps run on Atlassian Forge. No external servers, no data leaving your instance. Your data stays yours.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Keep it simple</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">We don't over-engineer. Our tools solve specific problems well, without unnecessary complexity or feature bloat.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Continuous improvement</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">Every app is actively maintained and improved based on real customer feedback and evolving Atlassian platform capabilities.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Our expertise</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-surface-raised border border-border rounded-lg p-5">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Consulting</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
                <li>Cloud migration</li>
                <li>Process optimization</li>
                <li>Infrastructure design</li>
                <li>Ongoing administration</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-raised border border-border rounded-lg p-5">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Development</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
                <li>Atlassian Forge apps</li>
                <li>Custom integrations</li>
                <li>Workflow automation</li>
                <li>API development</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-raised border border-border rounded-lg p-5">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Support</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
                <li>Service desk operations</li>
                <li>System maintenance</li>
                <li>Updates & migrations</li>
                <li>Team training</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
